00:26:54,450 --> 00:26:55,780
[Jinwoo: Because up until now,]

660
00:26:55,780 --> 00:26:58,990
[Jinwoo: Seungho was the only one
who had been choosing me.]

661
00:26:58,990 --> 00:27:01,920
[Jinwoo: So the moment Seungho picks someone else,]

662
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:05,930
[Jinwoo: I'm down to zero votes.]

663
00:27:05,930 --> 00:27:08,060
[Jinwoo: I prepared myself for it.]

664
00:27:08,060 --> 00:27:09,660
[Jinwoo: So Seungho and I]

665
00:27:09,660 --> 00:27:10,730
[Jinwoo: actually talked about that.]

666
00:27:10,730 --> 00:27:14,470
[Jinwoo: "If you want to pick someone else,
go for it. Don't feel tied down."]

667
00:27:14,470 --> 00:27:16,600
[Jinwoo: I told him that day, so]

668
00:27:16,600 --> 00:27:20,070
[Jinwoo: it felt a bit bitter, but that's about it.]

669
00:27:20,070 --> 00:27:23,550
[Jinwoo: No hard feelings.]

670
00:27:24,080 --> 00:27:27,280
[Nobody chose you today]

671
00:27:29,420 --> 00:27:33,420
[Yongkyu: I need to be more open about how I feel.]

672
00:27:33,420 --> 00:27:36,360
[Yongkyu: We did go on a date that day, after all.]

673
00:27:36,360 --> 00:27:38,760
[Yongkyu: We went together
because we were interested.]

674
00:27:38,760 --> 00:27:39,560
[Yongkyu: But getting zero votes]

675
00:27:39,560 --> 00:27:41,430
[Yongkyu: made my mind race.]

676
00:27:42,620 --> 00:27:45,430
[Yongkyu: Was the date just mediocre?]

677
00:27:45,430 --> 00:27:49,440
[Yongkyu: Did he think we just didn't click]

678
00:27:49,440 --> 00:27:52,910
[Yongkyu: because of the way]

679
00:27:52,910 --> 00:27:55,310
[Yongkyu: we talked during the date?]

680
00:28:01,980 --> 00:28:07,590
[Kim Seungho, Lim Chaebe, and Tae Eunchae chose you]
[You matched with Kim Seungho.]

681
00:28:10,260 --> 00:28:12,930
[Hyeyeon: We went on a date yesterday,]

682
00:28:12,930 --> 00:28:14,800
[Hyeyeon: but he didn't pick me. I got 0 votes.]

683
00:28:14,800 --> 00:28:18,270
[Hyeyeon: But today, unexpected people
voted for me.]

684
00:28:18,270 --> 00:28:20,400
[Hyeyeon: Even Seungho and I matched.]

685
00:28:20,400 --> 00:28:23,610
[Hyeyeon: Wait, what? Oh, awesome.]

686
00:28:24,670 --> 00:28:27,340
[Seungho: I already knew exactly
where Jinwoo stands.]

687
00:28:27,340 --> 00:28:29,740
[Seungho: But Hyeyeon
said she's torn between two people.]

688
00:28:29,740 --> 00:28:30,550
[Seungho: I was curious]

689
00:28:30,550 --> 00:28:33,480
[Seungho: whether I'm her first or second choice.]

690
00:28:33,480 --> 00:28:36,420
[Seungho: I wanted to talk to her again.]

691
00:28:36,420 --> 00:28:38,290
[Seungho: So I chose Hyeyeon.]

692
00:28:39,350 --> 00:28:43,090
[Eunchae: I only had eyes for Heejin at first.]

693
00:28:43,090 --> 00:28:45,490
[Eunchae: But after my first date with Hyeyeon,]

694
00:28:45,490 --> 00:28:49,500
[Eunchae: someone new came into the picture,
and I found her really interesting.

695
00:28:50,570 --> 00:28:53,770
[Chaebe: I chose Hyeyeon.]

696
00:28:53,770 --> 00:28:56,700
[Chaebe: Even though Yongkyu is my number 1,]

697
00:28:56,700 --> 00:28:59,910
[Chaebe: talking and joking around—]

698
00:28:59,910 --> 00:29:01,240
[Chaebe: She was the first person I did that with.]

699
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:05,250
[Chaebe: I thought, "Oh, she's great."]

700
00:29:05,250 --> 00:29:08,450
[Chaebe: So I picked her.]

701
00:29:08,980 --> 00:29:11,650
[Jinwoo: Who on earth is going?]

702
00:29:12,450 --> 00:29:13,900
[Jinwoo: Heart thumping]

703
00:29:14,060 --> 00:29:16,420
[Anxious]

704
00:29:16,420 --> 00:29:18,700
[Tense]

705
00:29:24,730 --> 00:29:34,340
[Tonight's Secret Room guests
are Kim Seungho and Kim Hyeyeon,
who tied for first place
and chose each other.]

706
00:29:41,020 --> 00:29:42,620
[Chaebe: Oh, so]

707
00:29:43,150 --> 00:29:46,090
[Chaebe: you are going?]
[Jinwoo: You're going to the Secret Room, right?]

708
00:29:48,490 --> 00:29:49,020
[Chaebe: Impressive.]

709
00:29:49,020 --> 00:29:52,230
[Jinwoo: Wow, incredible. Oh.]

710
00:29:52,760 --> 00:29:54,360
[Chaebe: Bring back some good food.]

711
00:29:55,430 --> 00:29:57,300
[Yongkyu: We have plenty of good food here.]

712
00:29:57,300 --> 00:29:59,430
[Sujin: Right, we have a lot here today.]
[Jinwoo: Yeah, we have a lot here too.]

713
00:29:59,430 --> 00:30:03,170
[Seungho: My stomach hurts,
so I might not eat much. I'll bring some back.]

714
00:30:04,770 --> 00:30:05,310
[Chaebe: Congrats.]

715
00:30:05,310 --> 00:30:08,780
[Jinwoo: Congrats.]

716
00:30:09,040 --> 00:30:10,380
[Hyeyeon: I was a bit overwhelmed.]

717
00:30:10,380 --> 00:30:13,310
[Hyeyeon: Seungho got 3 votes, and I got 3 votes.]

718
00:30:13,310 --> 00:30:15,980
[Hyeyeon: I was like, "Oh my god,
we even matched?"]

719
00:30:15,980 --> 00:30:18,650
[Hyeyeon: What is going on?
I was totally shocked.]

720
00:30:20,250 --> 00:30:24,530
[Seungho: They said a 4-year age gap
makes a perfect match.]

721
00:30:24,530 --> 00:30:25,860
[Seungho: That was one thing.]

722
00:30:25,860 --> 00:30:29,060
[Seungho: And career-wise,]

723
00:30:29,060 --> 00:30:33,070
[Seungho: I prefer someone I can relate to.]

724
00:30:33,070 --> 00:30:35,200
[Seungho: Hyeyeon probably has more]

725
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:38,940
[Seungho: in common with me]

726
00:30:38,940 --> 00:30:40,540
[Seungho: than Jinwoo does.]

727
00:30:41,610 --> 00:30:44,280
[Jinwoo: My heart just sank. And]

728
00:30:44,280 --> 00:30:46,150
[Jinwoo: they matched.]

729
00:30:46,150 --> 00:30:50,150
[Jinwoo: So did Seungho find Hyeyeon's]

730
00:30:50,150 --> 00:30:51,750
[Jinwoo: age and job]

731
00:30:51,750 --> 00:30:54,690
[Jinwoo: attractive?]

732
00:30:54,690 --> 00:30:58,690
[Jinwoo: Or did he vote for Hyeyeon knowing]

733
00:30:58,690 --> 00:31:01,100
[Jinwoo: this vote was]

734
00:31:01,100 --> 00:31:03,770
[Jinwoo: for the Secret Room?]

735
00:31:04,300 --> 00:31:06,700
[Hyeyeon: We'll be right back.]
[Jinwoo: Go ahead.]

736
00:31:06,700 --> 00:31:09,640
[Heejin: Have fun.]
[Chaebe: Bring good food.]

737
00:31:11,510 --> 00:31:14,980
[Heejin: What do I do? What do I do...
I really don't know anymore.]

738
00:31:14,980 --> 00:31:17,110
[Heejin: I genuinely don't know.]

739
00:31:21,120 --> 00:31:23,790
[Sujin: Even though I have a single room,]

740
00:31:23,790 --> 00:31:26,990
[Sujin: private chats are still limited.]

741
00:31:26,990 --> 00:31:30,460
[Sujin: In the Secret Room, you get great food]

742
00:31:30,460 --> 00:31:32,590
[Sujin: and drinks.]

743
00:31:32,590 --> 00:31:37,130
[Sujin: I wondered if they'd
have a more honest conversation.]

744
00:31:37,130 --> 00:31:39,270
[Sujin: I want to go to the Secret Room, too.]

745
00:31:39,270 --> 00:31:41,400
[Sujin: It would be great]

746
00:31:41,400 --> 00:31:43,270
[Sujin: to go with Heejin.]

747
00:31:44,340 --> 00:31:48,080
[Chaebe: Going there must
give off a totally different vibe.]

748
00:31:48,080 --> 00:31:50,210
[Chaebe: I really wanted to go.]

749
00:31:50,210 --> 00:31:53,410
[Chaebe: But now, I'm not that jealous.]

750
00:31:53,410 --> 00:31:56,080
[Chaebe: I already went on a date.]

751
00:31:56,080 --> 00:31:58,750
[Chaebe: No regrets. Compared to anyone else,]

752
00:31:58,750 --> 00:32:01,690
[Chaebe: I had a highly]

753
00:32:01,690 --> 00:32:03,290
[Chaebe: satisfying day.]

754
00:32:03,290 --> 00:32:08,100
[Chaebe: Why do I need to go there anyway?
He's right next to me.]

755
00:32:08,630 --> 00:32:12,630
[Hyeyeon: Does your stomach hurt?]
[Seungho: Better than before.]

756
00:32:12,630 --> 00:32:18,100
[Hyeyeon: Badly?]
[Seungho: A little bit, on and off.]

757
00:32:20,220 --> 00:32:22,240
[Hyeyeon: What should we bring?
You've been there.]

758
00:32:22,240 --> 00:32:24,340
[Seungho: Nothing, just...
Ah, I only brought my bag last time.]

759
00:32:24,340 --> 00:32:28,120
[Hyeyeon: We can always come back
for whatever we need.]
[Seungho: Yeah, let's pack light.]

760
00:32:28,120 --> 00:32:31,050
[Hyeyeon: Okay, I'll pack light, too.]

761
00:32:32,120 --> 00:32:34,260
[Hyeyeon: We matched today]

762
00:32:34,260 --> 00:32:36,120
[Hyeyeon: and went to the Secret Room together.]

763
00:32:36,120 --> 00:32:38,790
[Hyeyeon: But hearts can change.]

764
00:32:38,790 --> 00:32:42,530
[Hyeyeon: I just hoped we would get closer tonight]

765
00:32:42,530 --> 00:32:46,530
[Hyeyeon: by spending time together
in the Secret Room.]

766
00:32:46,800 --> 00:32:50,000
[Jinwoo: We have the place to ourselves tonight.]

767
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:53,210
[Heejin: Ah, I... but it's just... it's just...]

768
00:32:53,210 --> 00:32:54,540
[Heejin: Two people are missing.]

769
00:32:54,540 --> 00:32:57,480
[Heejin: "Hey, I can shower early tonight."]
[Jinwoo: Oh, exactly.]

770
00:32:58,550 --> 00:33:00,950
[Staring]
[Jinwoo: This is our Secret Room.]

771
00:33:05,750 --> 00:33:08,960
[Hyeyeon: Um... I'm going to grab my charger.]

772
00:33:08,960 --> 00:33:13,760
[Jinwoo: Go eat lots of good food.]
[Hyeyeon: But his stomach hurts,
and my throat hurts.]

773
00:33:13,760 --> 00:33:18,030
[Jinwoo: No drinking then.]
[Hyeyeon: It's a hospital ward
in the Secret Room tonight.]

774
00:33:18,030 --> 00:33:20,430
[Jinwoo: Then don't drink too much.]
[Seungho: But we can both hold our liquor.]

775
00:33:20,430 --> 00:33:21,770
[Hyeyeon: Yeah.]
[Seungho: Just a bit.]

776
00:33:21,770 --> 00:33:22,570
[Jinwoo: Got it.]

777
00:33:25,240 --> 00:33:29,240
[Seungho looks a bit conflicted]

778
00:33:29,240 --> 00:33:32,180
[Seungho: On the first day, I picked him]

779
00:33:32,180 --> 00:33:34,320
[Seungho: to go to the Secret Room.]

780
00:33:34,320 --> 00:33:38,320
[Seungho: But this time, Hyeyeon and I tied for first,]

781
00:33:38,320 --> 00:33:40,990
[Seungho: so we went together.]

782
00:33:40,990 --> 00:33:42,320
[Seungho: I actually felt relieved.]

783
00:33:42,320 --> 00:33:46,060
[Seungho: I didn't have to worry as much
about how Jinwoo felt.]

784
00:33:47,130 --> 00:33:49,530
[Jinwoo: Honestly, I minded it a lot.]

785
00:33:49,530 --> 00:33:52,200
[Jinwoo: I had so many questions for him.]

786
00:33:52,200 --> 00:33:53,530
[Jinwoo: And my thoughts were all over the place.]

787
00:33:53,530 --> 00:33:57,000
[Jinwoo: I didn't want to show my inner chaos,]

788
00:33:57,000 --> 00:33:59,140
[Jinwoo: so I just forced a smile]

789
00:33:59,140 --> 00:34:03,140
[Jinwoo: and told them to eat well.]

790
00:34:04,210 --> 00:34:07,150
[Hyeyeon and Seungho are getting ready]

791
00:34:07,150 --> 00:34:11,150
[Heejin completely ignores them]

792
00:34:11,949 --> 00:34:14,620
[Hyeyeon: Should I dress up a bit?
It is the Secret Room, after all.]

793
00:34:14,620 --> 00:34:17,560
[Seungho: A... a little bit... more than this?]

794
00:34:17,560 --> 00:34:20,760
[Hyeyeon: Got it.]

795
00:34:21,830 --> 00:34:25,570
[Heejin: Sighs. Oh man...]

796
00:34:25,570 --> 00:34:29,300
[Heejin: Ah... no one...]

797
00:34:29,300 --> 00:34:31,170
[Heejin: Seriously.]

798
00:34:33,570 --> 00:34:38,380
[Heejin hides under the covers]

799
00:34:38,380 --> 00:34:42,650
[Heejin: Hyeyeon wasn't the right person for me.
If that path didn't work,]

800
00:34:42,650 --> 00:34:47,190
[Heejin: I still had other options.]

801
00:34:47,190 --> 00:34:49,590
[Heejin: But even those choices]

802
00:34:49,590 --> 00:34:52,790
[Heejin: vanished one by one.]

803
00:34:52,790 --> 00:34:56,000
[Heejin: I had no one left to choose.]

804
00:34:56,000 --> 00:34:59,730
[Heejin: I never imagined I'd cry.]

805
00:34:59,730 --> 00:35:03,470
[Heejin: Ah... seriously.]

806
00:35:03,470 --> 00:35:08,660
[Heejin: Ugh, can they please edit this part out?]

807
00:35:11,740 --> 00:35:16,020
[Excited] [Excited]

808
00:35:18,150 --> 00:35:22,960
[Hyeyeon is thrilled
about the long-awaited alone time with Seungho]

809
00:35:23,220 --> 00:35:28,300
[Meanwhile, Eunchae and Sujin
run into each other in the living room]

810
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:32,300
[Sujin: What? What? What?]
[Eunchae: Ah, what a surprise.]

811
00:35:32,300 --> 00:35:34,170
[Eunchae: So interesting.]
[Sujin: Girls' night?]

812
00:35:34,170 --> 00:35:37,370
[Eunchae: Down?]
[Sujin: Girls' night? You down?]

813
00:35:37,370 --> 00:35:39,240
[Eunchae: This is getting so interesting.]
[Sujin: What's interesting?]

814
00:35:39,240 --> 00:35:40,840
[Eunchae: The Secret Room. Huge plot twist.]

815
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:42,440
[Eunchae: Such a twist.]

816
00:35:42,440 --> 00:35:45,910
[Sujin: Why? Why? Why?
Anyone watching could tell.]

817
00:35:45,910 --> 00:35:47,780
[Sujin: During the Truth Game.]

818
00:35:47,780 --> 00:35:50,180
[Eunchae: Ah, really? Yesterday?]
[Sujin: Yeah, yeah.]

819
00:35:50,180 --> 00:35:52,850
[Eunchae: Huh? I had no idea.]

820
00:35:52,850 --> 00:35:56,320
[Sujin: Seungho asked Hyeyeon,]

821
00:35:56,320 --> 00:35:58,660
[Sujin: "In the arrow date,]

822
00:35:58,660 --> 00:35:59,260
[Ah...]
[Sujin: "In the arrow date,]

823
00:35:59,260 --> 00:36:00,940
[Ah...]
[Sujin: if you could pick a girl,
would you still pick me?" And Hyeyeon said—]

824
00:36:00,940 --> 00:36:03,530
[Sujin: if you could pick a girl,
would you still pick me?" And Hyeyeon said—]

825
00:36:04,870 --> 00:36:07,540
[Sujin: He asked if she'd still pick him
if girls were an option.]

826
00:36:07,540 --> 00:36:09,400
[Sujin: And she said yes.]

827
00:36:09,400 --> 00:36:12,070
[Eunchae: Oh, I thought she was just being polite.]

828
00:36:12,070 --> 00:36:13,670
[Eunchae: I didn't realize they were that far along.]

829
00:36:13,670 --> 00:36:16,340
[Sujin: No, Hyeyeon is split down the middle.]

830
00:36:16,340 --> 00:36:18,480
[Sujin: Half of her heart is for one guy—]

831
00:36:18,480 --> 00:36:23,550
[Sujin: that's Seungho.
Seungho also said it was more like a 60-40 split.]

832
00:36:23,550 --> 00:36:27,820
[Sujin: I feel like the 60 is Jinwoo
and the 40 is Hyeyeon.]
[Eunchae: But, this time they wanted to go together.]

833
00:36:27,820 --> 00:36:29,960
[Sujin: Seungho wanted to go with Hyeyeon.]

834
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:31,560
[Sujin: If Seungho won the vote,]

835
00:36:31,560 --> 00:36:34,500
[Sujin: he'd definitely pick Hyeyeon.]

836
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:36,100
[Eunchae: I get it now.]
[Sujin: Huh?]

837
00:36:36,100 --> 00:36:37,970
[Eunchae: Makes sense.]
[Sujin: You got it?]

838
00:36:37,970 --> 00:36:40,630
[Eunchae: What shocked me was]

839
00:36:40,630 --> 00:36:43,570
[Eunchae: that during the anonymous chat room,
nobody joined mine.]

840
00:36:43,570 --> 00:36:46,510
[Sujin: Seriously?]
[Eunchae: Yeah.]

841
00:36:46,510 --> 00:36:50,240
[Sujin: Aw, you must've been so hurt that day.]
[Eunchae: Yeah, that's why you sent a message]

842
00:36:50,240 --> 00:36:53,450
[Eunchae: asking me, "How is it?" But—]

843
00:36:54,100 --> 00:36:55,580
[Chaebe: What are you talking about?]

844
00:36:55,580 --> 00:36:59,050
[Eunchae: Something fun. Super interesting.]
[Sujin: Juice. Juicy gossip.
You down? Juicy gossip, down?]

845
00:36:59,050 --> 00:37:00,390
[Eunchae: Something super interesting.]
[Yongkyu: What is it? What is it?]

846
00:37:00,390 --> 00:37:03,140
[Chaebe: I want to hear, too.]

847
00:37:05,380 --> 00:37:07,620
[Sighs...]

848
00:37:07,620 --> 00:37:08,930
[Chaebe: What is it?]

849
00:37:10,260 --> 00:37:12,130
[Chaebe: What is it?]

850
00:37:13,000 --> 00:37:18,270
[This is Day 3.]
[Sujin: The Secret Room vote...
is it who I think it is?]

851
00:37:18,270 --> 00:37:19,610
[Yongkyu: Did you smoke?]
[Eunchae: Not yet.]

852
00:37:19,610 --> 00:37:21,640
[Go ahead]

853
00:37:23,610 --> 00:37:25,610
[Chaebe: Who is it?]

854
00:37:25,610 --> 00:37:27,620
[Sujin: In the secret room, did you
vote for that person I know?]

855
00:37:27,620 --> 00:37:30,280
[Sujin: Today?]
[Chaebe: Today? No.]

856
00:37:30,280 --> 00:37:33,220
[Sujin: Who?]
[Chaebe: Someone else.]

857
00:37:33,220 --> 00:37:34,560
[Sujin: Oh, you can't just tell me directly.]

858
00:37:34,560 --> 00:37:36,420
[Sujin: No, it's fine actually.]

859
00:37:34,660 --> 00:37:36,590
-No, it's fine. -It's fine.

860
00:37:36,420 --> 00:37:37,760
[Chaebe: I voted for Hyeyeon.]

861
00:37:37,760 --> 00:37:40,430
[Sujin: Why? Because you're curious about her?]

862
00:37:40,430 --> 00:37:43,900
[Chaebe: Curious? I don't know.
It's just a little...]

863
00:37:43,900 --> 00:37:46,030
[Chaebe: It was fun. During
the cooking earlier...]

864
00:37:46,030 --> 00:37:48,830
[Chaebe: I thought, "Oh, it would be fun
to hang out with her."]

865
00:37:48,830 --> 00:37:51,640
[Sujin: You wanted to talk to her.]

866
00:37:51,640 --> 00:37:53,770
[Chaebe: I thought it'd be fun, so I picked her.]

867
00:37:56,440 --> 00:37:58,580
[Sujin: How was your date today?]

868
00:37:58,580 --> 00:38:00,710
[Chaebe: The date? I had a really good time.]

869
00:38:00,710 --> 00:38:04,720
[Sujin: You already liked her this much. Do you
like her even more now? Your feelings.]

870
00:38:04,720 --> 00:38:07,660
[Chaebe: I already had some feelings for her.]

871
00:38:07,660 --> 00:38:09,260
[Sujin: If 10 is the max...]

872
00:38:09,260 --> 00:38:11,660
[Sujin: If 100 is 10, and 10 means
you really like them...]

873
00:38:11,660 --> 00:38:14,060
[Sujin: then what was it before? Like a 2?]

874
00:38:14,060 --> 00:38:15,660
[Chaebe: Before...]

875
00:38:15,660 --> 00:38:19,130
[Chaebe: I already liked her quite a bit.]

876
00:38:19,030 --> 00:38:20,490
-But... -About a 5?

877
00:38:19,130 --> 00:38:21,540
[Sujin: About a 5?]
[Chaebe: Yeah.]

878
00:38:21,540 --> 00:38:25,270
[Chaebe: But after the date,
I liked her even more.]

879
00:38:25,270 --> 00:38:32,210
[Chaebe: So I think if we hadn't gone on
a date today, it wouldn't have worked out.]

880
00:38:32,210 --> 00:38:35,680
[Chaebe: So I'm really happy with today.]
[Sujin: But why?]

881
00:38:35,680 --> 00:38:36,880
[Chaebe: Because I'm still curious.]

882
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:38,090
[Sujin: You want to know more.
You need to know more.]

883
00:38:38,090 --> 00:38:42,090
[Chaebe: Other people too... and...]
[Sujin: Right, right, right.]

884
00:38:42,090 --> 00:38:47,700
[Chaebe: Anyway, that guy doesn't seem
to like me much.]

885
00:38:47,700 --> 00:38:49,830
[Sujin: Why?]
[Chaebe: You can tell right away.]

886
00:38:49,830 --> 00:38:54,370
[Chaebe: Because we've been talking a lot]

887
00:38:54,370 --> 00:38:56,770
[Chaebe: and he even said in front of me]

888
00:38:56,770 --> 00:39:02,380
[Chaebe: that he's interested
in someone else. So I thought]

889
00:39:02,380 --> 00:39:06,380
[Chaebe: he wouldn't even consider me.]

890
00:39:06,380 --> 00:39:10,380
[Chaebe: So I just let it go.]

891
00:39:10,380 --> 00:39:13,590
[Chaebe: I don't know. Who did you pick?]

892
00:39:13,590 --> 00:39:16,790
[Sujin: I picked you.]

893
00:39:17,190 --> 00:39:18,320
No, wait...

894
00:39:21,060 --> 00:39:24,000
[Sujin: No, that's because]

895
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:25,600
[Sujin: I originally...]

896
00:39:25,600 --> 00:39:30,940
[Sujin: I originally liked Heejin.]

897
00:39:30,940 --> 00:39:34,680
[Sujin: But after today's date,
it felt just okay.]

898
00:39:35,740 --> 00:39:37,500
[Sujin: It was neither here nor there...]
[Chaebe: No spark?]

899
00:39:37,500 --> 00:39:41,080
[Sujin: It's not that there was no spark.
It was fun and enjoyable.]

900
00:39:41,080 --> 00:39:45,090
[Sujin: But during the introduction...]

901
00:39:45,090 --> 00:39:46,420
[Sujin: Heejin said she wants to date men.]

902
00:39:46,420 --> 00:39:50,960
[Chaebe: Oh... Oh... really?]

903
00:39:50,960 --> 00:39:55,230
[Heejin: Right now, I'm more... the gender
I want to date more is men.]

904
00:39:55,230 --> 00:39:57,900
[Heejin: Even though it's men, here...]

905
00:39:57,900 --> 00:40:01,900
[Heejin: I can have feelings for both men
and women. The ratio is the same.]

906
00:40:01,900 --> 00:40:05,370
[Sujin: Even though she said it's fifty-fifty...]

907
00:40:05,370 --> 00:40:08,040
[Sujin: it still feels a little...]

908
00:40:08,310 --> 00:40:11,780
[While Sujin and Chaebe are sharing
their true feelings]

909
00:40:14,980 --> 00:40:16,850
[Jinwoo: What's going on? What's going on?]

910
00:40:18,450 --> 00:40:20,320
[Eunchae: How was it?]

911
00:40:20,320 --> 00:40:22,190
[Yongkyu: It was fun.]
[Eunchae: I thought so too.]

912
00:40:22,190 --> 00:40:24,940
[Jinwoo: Now that we know everything,
it's even more interesting.]

913
00:40:24,980 --> 00:40:28,540
[At this moment, I can't help but smile]

914
00:40:28,600 --> 00:40:30,460
[Eunchae: At this stage, I like Hyeyeon.]

915
00:40:30,460 --> 00:40:34,200
[Eunchae: When we revealed ages
and occupations today,]

916
00:40:34,200 --> 00:40:35,800
[Eunchae: I realized that the age gap
between Heejin and me]

917
00:40:35,800 --> 00:40:39,270
[Eunchae: is 9 years. It's quite big.]

918
00:40:39,270 --> 00:40:41,680
[Eunchae: And the things I talked about
with Hyeyeon...]

919
00:40:41,680 --> 00:40:44,080
[Eunchae: are exactly the kind of
conversations I enjoy.]

920
00:40:44,080 --> 00:40:47,550
[Eunchae: Plus, our ages are more compatible.]

921
00:40:47,550 --> 00:40:50,220
[Eunchae: So right now, I like Hyeyeon more.]

922
00:40:50,220 --> 00:40:54,220
[Eunchae: But later, if I get another chance
to go on a date with Heejin...]

923
00:40:54,220 --> 00:40:56,090
[Eunchae: I might not consider age as a factor.]

924
00:40:56,090 --> 00:41:00,090
[Eunchae: My feelings could change.]

925
00:41:01,860 --> 00:41:04,580
[The secret room door opens]

926
00:41:05,660 --> 00:41:09,060
[Hyeyeon and Seungho are about to enjoy
some time alone together]

927
00:41:10,340 --> 00:41:11,700
[Run, run]

928
00:41:14,100 --> 00:41:16,700
[Lively]

929
00:41:16,700 --> 00:41:17,660
[Looking down]

930
00:41:17,660 --> 00:41:20,380
[Looking down]
[Seungho: I think someone... someone's coming.]

931
00:41:19,800 --> 00:41:20,830
-Right? -Yeah.

932
00:41:20,830 --> 00:41:21,890
Like a goat.

933
00:41:23,110 --> 00:41:24,360
Could it be like that?

934
00:41:24,120 --> 00:41:28,120
[Just then, they run into Yongkyu,
Jinwoo, and Eunchae]

935
00:41:24,980 --> 00:41:26,330
You've heard of the Joker, right?

936
00:41:26,330 --> 00:41:27,520
You've heard of the Joker, right?

937
00:41:27,520 --> 00:41:28,380
I've heard of it.

938
00:41:28,380 --> 00:41:29,780
Looks like they're going there.

939
00:41:28,660 --> 00:41:30,520
[Jinwoo: Looks like they're going there.]

940
00:41:30,520 --> 00:41:32,390
[Eunchae: Oh no. This is bad.]

941
00:41:32,390 --> 00:41:34,800
[Eunchae: Oh, seriously...]

942
00:41:35,430 --> 00:41:36,870
Oh no. This is bad.

943
00:41:36,870 --> 00:41:38,140
Oh, seriously.

944
00:41:42,660 --> 00:41:44,670
[Hyeyeon: She said, "Oh no. This is bad."]

945
00:41:45,100 --> 00:41:47,700
[Hyeyeon: So the secret room is that
scary of a place?]

946
00:41:47,700 --> 00:41:49,300
[Seungho: The first day was fine since
it was the first day...]

947
00:41:49,300 --> 00:41:50,900
[Hyeyeon: Right, because everyone didn't know
each other well yet.]

948
00:41:50,900 --> 00:41:53,300
[Hyeyeon: Back then, I thought, "I'm so jealous."]

949
00:41:53,300 --> 00:41:56,770
[Hyeyeon: Now that everyone's feelings
are confirmed, walking into this room]

950
00:41:56,770 --> 00:41:58,910
[Hyeyeon: feels like going to prison
or something?]

951
00:42:01,580 --> 00:42:04,510
[Hyeyeon: No one else is here,
and no one will come in either.]

952
00:42:04,510 --> 00:42:09,050
[Hyeyeon: In this space with no time limit,
where we can talk freely...]

953
00:42:09,050 --> 00:42:12,520
[Hyeyeon: I need to be more proactive
and more forward]

954
00:42:12,520 --> 00:42:13,860
[Hyeyeon: so we could get closer.]

955
00:42:13,860 --> 00:42:17,330
[Hyeyeon: I hope this becomes
an opportunity for that.]

956
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:19,730
[Seungho: Did something change?]

957
00:42:19,730 --> 00:42:22,400
[Seungho: The cushion looks different?]

958
00:42:22,400 --> 00:42:24,000
[Hyeyeon: Is it softer now?]

959
00:42:24,270 --> 00:42:26,140
[Seungho: Sparkling wine?]

960
00:42:26,140 --> 00:42:26,940
[Seungho: Now it's a whole bottle.]

961
00:42:26,940 --> 00:42:29,870
[Hyeyeon: Isn't this wine way too light for us?]

962
00:42:30,060 --> 00:42:31,420
[Haha]

963
00:42:31,580 --> 00:42:35,210
[Seungho: I went to the secret room
on the first day, right?]

964
00:42:35,210 --> 00:42:38,950
[Seungho: I didn't expect to get picked again.
Anyway, I'm in a great mood.]

965
00:42:38,950 --> 00:42:42,820
[Seungho: This time, I want to ask more
about things I've been curious about.]

966
00:42:43,540 --> 00:42:45,460
[Hyeyeon: How do you open this?]

967
00:42:45,530 --> 00:42:47,990
The one from last time seems a little
different from this one.

968
00:42:45,740 --> 00:42:49,630
[The two decide to have some white wine first]

969
00:42:47,990 --> 00:42:50,250
-I think you just twist it open. -Really?

970
00:42:50,660 --> 00:42:52,660
[Struggling]

971
00:42:52,940 --> 00:42:53,100
Right.

972
00:42:53,100 --> 00:42:56,830
[Seungho: Isn't there one this time? Like
a corkscrew or something?]

973
00:42:57,370 --> 00:42:59,240
[Hyeyeon: It's a cork.]

974
00:42:59,240 --> 00:43:00,840
[Seungho: Do you know how to do this?]

975
00:43:00,840 --> 00:43:03,240
[Seungho: Actually, I didn't open it last time.
Jinwoo did everything...]

976
00:43:04,040 --> 00:43:07,240
[Hyeyeon: Then I have to do it? Let me try.]

977
00:43:07,240 --> 00:43:08,580
[Hyeyeon: I can't lose.]

978
00:43:10,180 --> 00:43:11,780
[Hyeyeon: Oh, I got it.]

979
00:43:13,380 --> 00:43:14,720
[Hyeyeon: This feels like an escape room.]

980
00:43:16,140 --> 00:43:17,940
[Pop!]

981
00:43:19,260 --> 00:43:21,140
[Startled]

982
00:43:23,260 --> 00:43:24,860
[Seungho: Oh, wait.]

983
00:43:24,860 --> 00:43:27,000
[Seungho: That was scary.]

984
00:43:27,000 --> 00:43:29,130
[Seungho: I panicked. It was so sudden.]

985
00:43:28,160 --> 00:43:28,930
Me too.

986
00:43:29,130 --> 00:43:31,540
[Seungho: I thought it was going to hit me.]

987
00:43:31,230 --> 00:43:32,490
Let's pick it up first.

988
00:43:35,010 --> 00:43:36,870
[Hyeyeon: Just a little bit.]

989
00:43:39,010 --> 00:43:40,610
[Hyeyeon: Seungho, by the way...]

990
00:43:40,610 --> 00:43:42,210
[Hyeyeon: Do you mind if people don't call you
by your name and just say "hey"?]

991
00:43:42,210 --> 00:43:44,080
[Seungho: I don't really like it.]
[Hyeyeon: Then should I call you Seungho?]

992
00:43:44,080 --> 00:43:47,280
[Seungho: But that does sound more
natural when spoken.]

993
00:43:47,280 --> 00:43:52,090
[Seungho: But since there's no final choice yet,
this much is fine.]

994
00:43:52,090 --> 00:43:54,490
[Hyeyeon: I'll keep that in mind.]

995
00:43:54,490 --> 00:43:55,560
[Seungho: Should we have a drink first?]

996
00:43:55,560 --> 00:43:57,430
[Hyeyeon: Should we clink glasses?]

997
00:44:01,700 --> 00:44:03,570
[Hyeyeon: Don't finish it all at once.]

998
00:44:02,250 --> 00:44:03,060
Okay.

999
00:44:03,570 --> 00:44:04,630
[Hyeyeon: Oh, this is good.]

1000
00:44:04,630 --> 00:44:07,040
[Seungho: Yeah, it has a hint of lemon?]

1001
00:44:07,040 --> 00:44:09,170
[Hyeyeon: 9% alcohol.]

1002
00:44:09,170 --> 00:44:12,110
[Seungho: Somewhere between beer and soju?]

1003
00:44:13,180 --> 00:44:16,780
[Seungho: Should we just talk first? For a while?]

1004
00:44:17,260 --> 00:44:19,180
[Hyeyeon: Today I really felt like a criminal.]

1005
00:44:19,180 --> 00:44:22,620
[Hyeyeon: The moment I heard Eunchae
say "This is bad"...]

1006
00:44:22,900 --> 00:44:24,500
[Fidgeting nervously]

1007
00:44:24,500 --> 00:44:26,060
[Hyeyeon: But what I find unfair is]

1008
00:44:26,060 --> 00:44:29,260
[Hyeyeon: the vibe of our date wasn't
so much about butterflies]

1009
00:44:29,260 --> 00:44:32,020
[Hyeyeon: as it was about a sense of closeness.]

1010
00:44:32,020 --> 00:44:33,780
[Hyeyeon: I think Eunchae just felt that.]

1011
00:44:33,780 --> 00:44:36,570
[Hyeyeon: We had a good time together today.]

1012
00:44:37,100 --> 00:44:40,860
[Hyeyeon: But Jinwoo...]

1013
00:44:40,630 --> 00:44:41,040
Right.

1014
00:44:40,860 --> 00:44:44,100
[Hyeyeon: he's been so direct in expressing
his feelings for you.]

1015
00:44:45,640 --> 00:44:47,140
[Seungho: So...]

1016
00:44:47,140 --> 00:44:50,180
[Seungho: I couldn't even look him
in the eye just now...]

1017
00:44:51,520 --> 00:44:53,650
[Hyeyeon: But honestly, today]

1018
00:44:53,650 --> 00:44:56,320
[Hyeyeon: I didn't think you'd pick me.]

1019
00:44:55,760 --> 00:44:56,390
So...

1020
00:44:56,320 --> 00:44:58,190
[Seungho: Me neither. Really.]

1021
00:44:58,190 --> 00:45:00,060
[Hyeyeon: The feeling was mutual? But why
did you pick me?]

1022
00:45:00,590 --> 00:45:01,930
[Seungho: I don't know. I just wanted to?]

1023
00:45:01,930 --> 00:45:03,260
[Hyeyeon: Did you just pick randomly?]

1024
00:45:03,260 --> 00:45:04,330
[Seungho: Not really.]

1025
00:45:04,600 --> 00:45:06,460
[Hyeyeon: As ESTPs...]

1026
00:45:06,460 --> 00:45:09,400
[Hyeyeon: so we don't make a losing deal...]

1027
00:45:09,400 --> 00:45:10,730
[Hyeyeon: shouldn't we be calculating?]

1028
00:45:10,730 --> 00:45:11,540
[Seungho: I did plenty of calculating.]

1029
00:45:12,070 --> 00:45:14,470
[Hyeyeon: Today I really thought you
wouldn't pick me.]

1030
00:45:14,470 --> 00:45:16,340
[Hyeyeon: If I confessed everything,]

1031
00:45:17,140 --> 00:45:20,880
[Hyeyeon: it would only make Jinwoo's
feelings for you stronger.]

1032
00:45:20,880 --> 00:45:24,080
[Hyeyeon: So it felt like Jinwoo
was protecting you]

1033
00:45:24,080 --> 00:45:27,020
[Hyeyeon: and building an invisible wall
around you.]

1034
00:45:27,020 --> 00:45:29,150
[Hyeyeon: I couldn't even get close to you today.]

1035
00:45:30,490 --> 00:45:35,290
[Hyeyeon was constantly worried
about Seungho's finger]

1036
00:45:35,290 --> 00:45:37,160
[Hyeyeon: Every time I tried to take care of you,]

1037
00:45:37,160 --> 00:45:39,300
[Hyeyeon: Jinwoo would show up!]

1038
00:45:39,300 --> 00:45:43,030
[Hyeyeon: When I heard you two were going on
a date alone, I felt something was off.]

1039
00:45:43,030 --> 00:45:48,370
[Hyeyeon: Jinwoo is very perceptive, especially
when it comes to you.]

1040
00:45:48,370 --> 00:45:52,380
[Hyeyeon: If Jinwoo saw the band-aid
I put on you,]

1041
00:45:52,380 --> 00:45:56,110
[Hyeyeon: you'd at least think for a moment:
Hyeyeon put this on. Should I tell Jinwoo?"]

1042
00:45:56,110 --> 00:45:58,520
[Hyeyeon: That's what I was thinking.]

1043
00:45:59,320 --> 00:46:00,920
[Hyeyeon: That was my plan.]

1044
00:46:02,520 --> 00:46:04,660
[Seungho: Yeah, I told him.]

1045
00:46:04,220 --> 00:46:04,710
You did?

1046
00:46:04,660 --> 00:46:06,260
[Seungho: Both the bracelet and the band-aid.
I told him about both.]

1047
00:46:07,740 --> 00:46:09,380
Haha.

1048
00:46:10,530 --> 00:46:12,660
[Hyeyeon: That's great.]

1049
00:46:12,660 --> 00:46:14,530
[Seungho: I was going to tell him anyway.]

1050
00:46:16,930 --> 00:46:21,200
[Hyeyeon: So it was a chance to further
confirm your feelings?]

1051
00:46:21,200 --> 00:46:24,140
[Seungho: You're right. And I was curious
about his reaction too.]

1052
00:46:24,140 --> 00:46:27,080
[Hyeyeon: Is it about the memories with me,
or the couple bracelet?]

1053
00:46:27,080 --> 00:46:30,550
[Hyeyeon: Or were you using it
to test the person you like?]

1054
00:46:30,550 --> 00:46:31,620
[Hyeyeon: Was I just a tool?]

1055
00:46:31,620 --> 00:46:34,020
[Seungho: No, no.]

1056
00:46:34,020 --> 00:46:36,690
[Hyeyeon: Right. Actually, I've been
confirming things too.]

1057
00:46:36,690 --> 00:46:38,020
[Hyeyeon: I thought you'd
take the bracelet off.]

1058
00:46:38,020 --> 00:46:39,890
[Hyeyeon: Especially when
going on a date.]

1059
00:46:39,890 --> 00:46:42,030
[Hyeyeon: Even if Jinwoo just said it
as a joke,]

1060
00:46:42,030 --> 00:46:44,700
[Hyeyeon: "Take off the bracelet since you're
on a date with me, OK?" If he said that,]

1061
00:46:44,700 --> 00:46:46,830
[Hyeyeon: you'd laugh and take it off.]

1062
00:46:47,630 --> 00:46:48,970
[Seungho: It's very likely if he said that.]

1063
00:46:49,160 --> 00:46:50,600
If he really said that...

1064
00:46:49,460 --> 00:46:50,700
[Disappointed]

1065
00:46:50,700 --> 00:46:52,440
[Disappointed
Seungho: But to be honest,]

1066
00:46:52,440 --> 00:46:54,300
[Seungho: Jinwoo isn't that kind of person.]

1067
00:46:54,300 --> 00:46:57,770
[Seungho: Even if I took it off then,
I'd put it right back on afterwards.]

1068
00:46:58,310 --> 00:47:01,240
[Hyeyeon: Really?
Seungho: I can guarantee this.]

1069
00:47:02,310 --> 00:47:06,050
[Hyeyeon: Did your heart flutter
during the date today?]

1070
00:47:06,580 --> 00:47:07,650
[Seungho: Yeah!]

1071
00:47:09,870 --> 00:47:10,140
I did.

1072
00:47:10,050 --> 00:47:12,460
[Hyeyeon: You answered way too quickly...]

1073
00:47:13,290 --> 00:47:15,660
You actually said yeah.

1074
00:47:20,730 --> 00:47:23,930
[Hyeyeon: Does your heart flutter
with me too?]

1075
00:47:25,000 --> 00:47:27,140
[Seungho: Yeah, it does.
Hyeyeon: Really?]

1076
00:47:26,450 --> 00:47:27,040
Yeah.

1077
00:47:27,610 --> 00:47:28,840
-Yeah, I did.
-Really?

1078
00:47:28,840 --> 00:47:29,680
Yeah.

1079
00:47:31,410 --> 00:47:33,280
[Hyeyeon: I totally didn't expect that.
Seungho: Why? Did you think it didn't?]

1080
00:47:33,280 --> 00:47:35,950
[Hyeyeon: I thought maybe it didn't.]

1081
00:47:35,950 --> 00:47:39,680
[Hyeyeon: Because I... didn't know
Seungho's feelings.]

1082
00:47:39,680 --> 00:47:42,350
[Hyeyeon: I didn't know.]

1083
00:47:43,690 --> 00:47:45,020
[Hyeyeon: Want a drink? Is this a penalty?]

1084
00:47:45,020 --> 00:47:46,620
[Seungho: It's not a penalty.]

1085
00:47:46,620 --> 00:47:48,760
[Seungho: It's a good chance.]

1086
00:47:49,560 --> 00:47:53,300
[Their time alone
is gradually heating up]

1087
00:47:54,900 --> 00:47:56,770
[Seungho: Am I close to your ideal type?]

1088
00:47:58,100 --> 00:48:00,770
[Seungho: No?
Hyeyeon: Actually, not really.]

1089
00:48:01,840 --> 00:48:03,970
[Seungho: Me neither.
Hyeyeon: Really?]

1090
00:48:04,240 --> 00:48:07,980
[Hyeyeon: Then among the girls living here,]

1091
00:48:07,980 --> 00:48:11,720
[Hyeyeon: whose appearance is closest
to your ideal type?]

1092
00:48:11,720 --> 00:48:14,120
[Hyeyeon: But the range is too broad.]

1093
00:48:15,450 --> 00:48:18,920
[Seungho: You are the closest.]

1094
00:48:15,680 --> 00:48:17,340
-You are the closest.
-Am I?

1095
00:48:18,920 --> 00:48:19,820
[Hyeyeon: Really?]

1096
00:48:19,820 --> 00:48:22,500
[Seungho: That means I don't have
a fixed ideal type.]

1097
00:48:22,500 --> 00:48:25,330
[Seungho: It depends on the person
and the feeling.]

1098
00:48:25,330 --> 00:48:28,530
[Hyeyeon: Yes. Everyone's ideal appearance
